/target
Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk

# This is a Rust repo — no npm. node_modules/ and a stray package.json once
# leaked in from an Azure MCP install (a 108MB binary that blew GitHub's
# 100MB push limit). Guard against a repeat.
node_modules/
package.json
package-lock.json
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Bot-orchestration artifacts. The overnight-chorale routine writes these
# locally; they hold raw decision ledgers, work-queue state, and pre-launch
# competitive recon. Belong in the maintainer's environment, not the public
# repo.
.overnight-chorale-*
docs/recon/

# Personal study notes Zach uses while reviewing in-flight design. Synthesizes
# the recon memos with Rust mechanics explanations; not part of the public
# documentation set. Regenerated after each implementation milestone with
# real code references pulled from chorale-core/src/ and chorale-dioxus/src/.
docs/v0.2.0-design-overview.md

# Local screen recordings (videos copied in for bot review, never tracked)
Screen Recording*.mov
*.mp4
examples/*/dist/
